author: Conor Gallagher
title: Coronavirus: 33 more people die from Covid-19 in the State bringing total to 320
description: Minister says HSE expects to clear Covid-19 testing backlog by next week
content:
A further 33 people have died of coronavirus in the Republic and 553 new cases have been confirmed as well as 286 new cases from a backlog sent to Germany, the National Public Health Emergency Team has said.
